	* goffice/utils/go-glib-extras.c (go_memdup_n): New function.

	* goffice/utils/go-spectre.c (go_spectre_load_data): Use go_memdup.

	* goffice/utils/go-emf.c (go_emf_load_data): Use go_memdup.
	(go_emf_new_from_data): Ditto.

