	go_memdup.

	* goffice/data/go-data-simple.c (go_data_vector_str_new_copy): Use
	g_new, not g_malloc.
	(go_data_vector_val_new_copy): Use go_memdup_n.

	* goffice/canvas/goc-group.c (goc_group_init): Use g_new0, not
	g_malloc0.

