2009-04-06  Emmanuel Pacaud <emmanuel.pacaud@lapp.in2p3.fr>

	Naming consistency fix.

	/\bGo([A-Z])/GO$1/
	/\bIS_GO_/GO_IS_/
	/\bIS_GOG_/GOG_IS_/
	/\bIS_GOD_/GOD_IS_/
	/\bGO_([A-Z,_]*)_TYPE\b/GO_TYPE_$1/
	/\bGOG_([A-Z,_]*)_TYPE\b/GOG_TYPE_$1/
	/\bGOD_([A-Z,_]*)_TYPE\b/GOD_TYPE_$1/

