	* graph/gog-renderer.c (gog_renderer_outline_size) : keep widths >= 1

	* graph/plugins/plot_barcol/gog-barcol.c (barcol_draw_rect) : clip to
	  integer sizes to decrease amount of bleed through due to antialiasing.

